$ Windows Mouse Appearance

Open mouse control panel:
code {
control main.cpl
code }

Change mouse pointer
code {
control main.cpl,,1
code }

{ Registry #mouse-registry

 Apparently, some mouse related configurations are stored in the → Windows/registry[Registry] under `/HKCU/ControlPanel/Mouse`.

}

sa:
  → http://ic.ims.hr/faq/winXP_commands/win_shortcut_commands.html
